---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ESD & Static Control Guides | Industrial Knowledge Base | DGSDK"
  description="ESD and static electricity guides for industrial manufacturing: what is ESD, how to prevent static shock, ESD control products, and industrial static eliminator solutions.">
  <section
    class="products-hero"
    style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.28), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18)), url('/assets/img/static-eliminator/bg-2.jpg') center/cover no-repeat; background-attachment: fixed;">
    <div class="container products-hero-inner">
      <span class="products-hero-kicker" data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-duration="600">Knowledge Base</span>
      <h1 data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="700" data-aos-delay="100">ESD & Static Control Guides</h1>
      <p data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="700" data-aos-delay="200">
        Technical guides on electrostatic discharge, static electricity prevention, and industrial static control
        for electronics, display, and industrial manufacturing environments.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:900px; padding: 60px 20px;">
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 28px;">

        <a href="/guides/what-is-esd" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0" data-aos-duration="600" style="display:block; padding:32px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:12px; text-decoration:none; color:inherit; transition: box-shadow 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10)'" onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='none'">
          <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem; margin:0 0 12px; color:#1a1a2e;">What Is ESD?</h2>
          <p style="margin:0; color:#555; font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6;">Electrostatic discharge explained — definition, causes, how ESD damages electronics, and industry standards for ESD control.</p>
          <span style="display:inline-block; margin-top:16px; color:#2563eb; font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:500;">Read guide →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/guides/how-to-prevent-static" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="80" data-aos-duration="600" style="display:block; padding:32px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:12px; text-decoration:none; color:inherit; transition: box-shadow 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10)'" onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='none'">
          <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem; margin:0 0 12px; color:#1a1a2e;">How to Prevent Static Electricity</h2>
          <p style="margin:0; color:#555; font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6;">Practical static electricity prevention methods: grounding, ionization, humidity control, ESD-safe materials, and operator procedures.</p>
          <span style="display:inline-block; margin-top:16px; color:#2563eb; font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:500;">Read guide →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/guides/esd-control-products" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="160" data-aos-duration="600" style="display:block; padding:32px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:12px; text-decoration:none; color:inherit; transition: box-shadow 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10)'" onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='none'">
          <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem; margin:0 0 12px; color:#1a1a2e;">ESD Control Products Guide</h2>
          <p style="margin:0; color:#555; font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6;">Buyer's guide to ESD control products — ionizing bars, ion blowers, ion rods, and how to select the right anti-static equipment for your application.</p>
          <span style="display:inline-block; margin-top:16px; color:#2563eb; font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:500;">Read guide →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/guides/industrial-static-eliminator" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="240" data-aos-duration="600" style="display:block; padding:32px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:12px; text-decoration:none; color:inherit; transition: box-shadow 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10)'" onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='none'">
          <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem; margin:0 0 12px; color:#1a1a2e;">Industrial Static Eliminator Solutions</h2>
          <p style="margin:0; color:#555; font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6;">Static eliminator applications by industry — electronics, display, printing, plastics, and cleanroom manufacturing, with product selection guidance.</p>
          <span style="display:inline-block; margin-top:16px; color:#2563eb; font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:500;">Read guide →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/guides/what-is-an-ionizing-bar" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="320" data-aos-duration="600" style="display:block; padding:32px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:12px; text-decoration:none; color:inherit; transition: box-shadow 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.10)'" onmouseout="this.style.boxShadow='none'">
          <h2 style="font-size:1.2rem; margin:0 0 12px; color:#1a1a2e;">What Is an Ionizing Bar?</h2>
          <p style="margin:0; color:#555; font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6;">How ionizer bars work, AC vs DC vs intelligent types, applications in electronics and display manufacturing, and how to choose the right ionizing bar.</p>
          <span style="display:inline-block; margin-top:16px; color:#2563eb; font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:500;">Read guide →</span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
